Subtivals, a program to project *.ass subtitles.

Subtivals goals are the projection and the control of subtitles on a cinema screen; for festivals that targets the hard of hearing.

Subtivals user interface is composed of two parts :
 - The subtitles "black box" that is projected
 - The control window that permits do load/play/pause/stop/add delay to the subtitles.

These two parts are intended to be show on two disctinctive screens in a Xinerama setup.

Subtivals is written in C++/Qt and has no other external dependencies.
